In the later stages of the [[Clone Wars]], the [[Dark Lord of the Sith|Dark Lord]] of the [[Sith]] [[Darth Sidious]], publicly known as [[Supreme Chancellor]] Palpatine of the [[Galactic Republic]], maintained a '''meditation chamber''' inside the [[Grand Republic Medical Facility]] on [[Coruscant]]. The [[meditation]] [[Meditation chamber|chamber]] notably contained a semicircle of padded couches, resembling Palpatine's most private office in the [[Imperial Executive Building|Senate Office Building]].<ref name="CL 2016" />

